# This directory stores agent-generated reports.
# Naming convention: <report-type>-<timestamp>.md
# Examples:
#   review-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md        — /review quality gate results
#   security-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md      — Security Engineer audit
#   e2e-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md           — QA E2E test report
#   benchmark-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md     — Performance benchmark
#   visual-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md        — Visual QA diff report
#   pipeline-audit-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md — CI/CD pipeline audit
#   postmortem-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md    — Incident postmortem
#   dataaudit-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md     — DB integrity audit
#   health-2026-01-15T10:30:00Z.md        — System health check
